 Alley (upcoming film)|Nightmare Alley]]''\n| TBA\n| Zeena Krumbein\n| Filming\n| <ref name=\"Kit\">{{cite news | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/toni-collette-joins-bradley-cooper-guillermo-del-toros-nightmare-alley-1239523 | title = Toni Collette Joins Bradley Cooper in Guillermo del Toro's ''Nightmare Alley'' | last = Kit | first = Borys | date = 13 September 2019 | work = The Hollywood Reporter | access-date = 9 April 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n===Television===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Role\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | {{Abbr|Ref.|Reference(s)}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[A Country Practice]]''\n| 1990\n| Tracy\n| Episode: \"The Sting: Part 1\"\n| <ref name=\"Dishinger\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''Ray Alexander: A Menu for Murder''\n| 1995\n| cast member\n| Television movie\n| <ref name=\"BFI Filmography\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''Exclusive!''\n| 1999\n| herself\n| Episodes (29/8/1999, 7/11/1999)\n| <ref name=\"BFI Filmography\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Dinner with Friends]]''\n| 2001\n| Beth\n| Television movie\n| <ref name=\"Flint Marx\"/><ref name=\"BFI Filmography\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[SMTV Live| SM:tv LIVE]]''\n| 2002\n| herself\n| Episode (27/4/2002)\n| <ref name=\"BFI Filmography\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[The Ellen DeGeneres Show]]''\n| 2003\n| herself\n| Season 1: Episode 60\n| <ref name=\"Metacritic TV list\"/><ref name=\"TVdb Season 1\">{{cite web | url = https://www.thetvdb.com/series/the-ellen-degeneres-show/seasons/official/1 | title = ''The Ellen DeGeneres Show'' - Official Order - Season 1 | work = TheTVDB.com | publisher = | date = | access-date = 9 April 2020 }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Tsunami: The Aftermath]]''\n| 2006\n| Kathy Graham\n| Television movie\n| <ref name=\"BFI Filmography\"/><ref name=\"Metacritic TV list\">{{cite web | url = https://