ice\n| [[Wharf Theatre]], [[Walsh Bay]]\n| align=\"center\"|<ref name=\"AusStage List\"/><ref name=\"Showcast\"/>\n|-\n| ''[[King Lear]]''\n| 1994\n| [[Cordelia (King Lear)|Cordelia]]\n| Drama Theatre, Sydney Opera House\n| align=\"center\"|<ref name=\"AusStage List\"/><ref name=\"Showcast\"/>\n|-\n| ''[[The Wild Party (LaChiusa musical)|The Wild Party]]''\n| 2000\n| Queenie\n| [[August Wilson Theatre|Virginia Theatre]], Broadway\n| align=\"center\"|<ref name=\"Showcast\"/><ref name=\"IBDB\">{{cite web | url = https://www.ibdb.com/broadway-cast-staff/toni-collette-75953 | title = Toni Collette \u2013 Broadway Cast & Staff | work = | publisher = [[Internet Broadway Database|IBDB]] | access-date = 11 April 2020 }}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[The Realistic Joneses]]''\n| 2014\n| Jennifer Jones\n| [[Lyceum Theatre (Broadway)|Lyceum Theatre]], Broadway\n| align=\"center\"|<ref name=\"Showcast\"/><ref name=\"IBDB\"/>\n|-\n|}\n\n==Discography==\n\n{{Main article|Toni Collette & the Finish}}\n* [[Toni Collette & the Finish]]: ''Beautiful Awkward Pictures'' (2006)&nbsp;\u2013 Hoola Hoop Records/[[MGM Distribution|MGM]] <small>(HOOLAHOOP002)</small>\n\n=== Other appearances ===\n\n* \"Best Friend\", \"Finale: The Wild Party\", \"People Like Us\" <small>(by Toni Collette and [[Yancey Arias]])</small>, \"Queenie Was a Blonde\", \"This Is What It Is\", \"Welcome to My Party\", \"Wild Party\" from ''The Wild Party: A Decca Original Broadway Cast Album'' (sountrack album, 2000)&nbsp;\u2013 [[Decca Broadway]]/[[Universal Music Group]] <small>(012 159 003-2)</small><ref name=\"Collar\"/>\n* \"Airport Medley: Oklahoma / Superstar / Papa Can You Hear Me? / Memory\", \"Let Me Entertain You\", \"[[Maybe This Time (song)|Maybe This Time]]\", \"Don't Rain on My Parade\", \"Medley: Everything's Alright / Don't Cry for Me\", \"[[I'm Gonna Wash That Man Right Outa My Hair]]\", \"There Is Nothing Like a Dame\", \"[[Cabaret (Cabaret song)|Cabaret]]\" <small>(all by [[Nia Vardalos]] and Toni Collette)</sm